how to make a detox tea for good health🎀🫶🏻

Beetroot Detox Tea Recipe

Ingredients:
1 teaspoon fennel seeds
1-2 cloves
1 small beetroot, grated
1-inch piece of ginger, grated
2 cups hot water
Juice of half a lemon
1-2 teaspoons honey (adjust to taste)

Instructions:
Simmer in Hot Water:
Pour 2 cups of hot water into the pot & add all ingredients
Bring the mixture to a gentle simmer over low heat.
Let it simmer for 10-15 minutes to infuse the flavors.

Strain and Serve:
Strain the tea into a glass or mug to remove the solids.

Add chia seeds 
Squeeze the juice of half a lemon into the tea.(optional)
Stir well to combine.
Sweeten with Honey(optional)
Add 1 teaspoons of honey, adjusting to your preferred sweetness.
